Author: Fargo
Title: [ANN] ITT Token - AI-enabled Crypto Trading Alerts
Body: We are excited to announce the launch of ITT's Facebook Bounty!  Please join and help spread the word about ITT!   Facebook Bounty  21,000 ITT tokens Rules Each member of Facebook Bounty campaign should have at least 300 friends In order to participate, each member should go through registration. Then, each member should follow the official ITT page https://www.facebook.com/ITT.Token/, like and follow the ITT Token page, and repost at least one ITT post per week. The bounty campaign timing is till the end of ITT Token Sale. In order to receive the bonus, each member is expected to participate till the end of the campaign. A member, who has not hit Like, or has not shared posts during one week, or unfollowed ITT Token official page is not eligible for a reward. The list of participants is being updated and analyzed once per week. Each accepted campaign member is to receive 1 share per week. After ITT Token Sale is finished, the whole ITT bounty pool is to be redistributed among all campaign members considering the number of shares each member has. Register here Monitor statistics here   Looking forward to having you on board!
